        ": \"أُمُّ اَلْوَلَدِ حَدُّهَا حَدُّ اَلْأَمَةِ إِذَا لَمْ يَكُنْ لَهَا وَلَدٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5053 - Ibn Mahbub narrated from Ali ibn Riʾab from Zurarah from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) who said:\n\"The prescribed punishment for Umm Al-Walad (a slave woman who has borne a child for her master) is the same as that of a slave woman if she has not borne a child.\""
        ]
      }
